META 1

Digital painting 
 
Metaverse Landscape. 
We invite you to explore the metaverse we created with our unique digitally hand carved architectural landscape.

Gentle lines hide among intense meshes, flowing freely they create a fabric of space or maybe a landscape of a distant meteorite?
Coming from years of architectural research in depth, each artwork is a carefully crafted abstract architectural space.

Each art work comes from a process that involves hand sculpting in different mediums, starting from physical sculpting and into a 3D digital hand sculpting.

The art work comes from the project Interface, that took more than 7500 hours to develop the project and methodology plus more than 250 hrs to finish one digitally hand sculpted landscape.

We invite you to experience our work in super HD quality and delve into the abstract worlds and futuristic landscapes.
